metadata.name: Human Being // V1
metadata.description:
The daily grind.

Each set is completely hand-built and crafted using a mixture of materials, including the seat patterns which are hand-drawn on felt. The puppet's figure is whittled from balsa wood in layers and glued together. All in all production, shooting and editing took 9 months to complete and was done by the songwriter (me), The Last Morrell.
